flowchart LR
    subgraph TODAY[Current state: all classical]
        direction TB
        C1[Data or problem] --> C2[Classical computer<br/>SVM, XGBoost, solver]
        C2 --> C3[Answer]
    end

    subgraph FUTURE[Target state: hybrid quantum-classical]
        direction TB
        F1[Data or problem] --> F2[Classical computer<br/>does most of the work]
        F2 --> F3[Quantum computer<br/>does one hard piece]
        F3 --> F2
        F2 --> F4[Answer]
    end

    TODAY -.wins today.-> WIN[Classical still wins<br/>on these tasks]
    FUTURE -.someday.-> HOPE[Quantum helps<br/>when hardware is quieter]

    style TODAY fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32
    style FUTURE fill:#EDE7F6,stroke:#4527A0
    style WIN fill:#E8F5E9,stroke:#2E7D32
    style HOPE fill:#EDE7F6,stroke:#4527A0
